[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/09/56/95693.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1176245","time":"2016-8-27 17:56","userId":"dangge","userName":"当歌","userSign":"(不易相处)","message":"最后一张图有趣。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/25/202532.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1176259","time":"2016-8-27 19:19","userId":"buernia","userName":"奈白不弍","userSign":"(我追番少，你可别骗我。)","message":"Johnston 作为一款经典的旧式无衬线字体，它跟 Gill Sans 的关系更近一些。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1176297","time":"2016-8-27 23:06","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"我不懂英文字体历史……<br><br>请问有没有关于英文字体字距的系统化资料？尤其是常用字符组合，我没有时间一对对测试。中文界好像不关注这方面。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/25/202532.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1176311","time":"2016-8-28 00:01","userId":"buernia","userName":"奈白不弍","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: 我不懂英文字体历史……<br><br>请问有没有关于英文字体字距的系统化资料？尤其是常用字符组合，我没有时间一对对测试。中文界好像不关注这方面。</q></div>最近出版了一本名叫<a href=\"https://book.douban.com/subject/26834548\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">《西文排版》</a>的书，里面有相关的内容。<br><br>或者打开一个字符比较多的正规西文字体查看 Kerning 信息也行。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1176386","time":"2016-8-28 17:48","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">奈白不弍</span> 说: 最近出版了一本名叫《西文排版》的书，里面有相关的内容。<br><br>或者打开一个字符比较多的正规西文字体查看 Kerning 信息也行。</q></div>后一种方法简单。<br><br>我正在看这本小册子：<a href=\"http://www.docin.com/p-485928900.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">http://www.docin.com/p-485928900.html</a>，感觉做英文字体比我想象的难。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/68/206873.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1176265","time":"2016-8-27 20:00","userId":"206873","userName":"Biourge","userSign":"(＝3)","message":"弱弱的觉得，【 i 】和【 ！】的点的菱形边不要向内凹会比较好看吧或许（最后一图 <img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/05.gif\" smileid=\"44\" alt=\"(bgm28)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1176294","time":"2016-8-27 23:04","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"没有向内凹，是错觉吧。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/68/206873.jpg","floor":"#4-2","id":"1176430","time":"2016-8-28 21:43","userId":"206873","userName":"Biourge","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: 没有向内凹，是错觉吧。</q></div>哦好像是的<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/25/202532.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1176936","time":"2016-9-1 08:19","userId":"buernia","userName":"奈白不弍","userSign":"(我追番少，你可别骗我。)","message":"知乎上找到了个相关的评论：<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/47891402/answer/108210548\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">伦敦地铁新字体 Johnston 100 与之前的 Johnston 相比有哪些改进？阿卡林的回答</a><div class=\"quote\"><q>按照 Monotype 的说法，这次的 Johnston 100 不是在 New Johnston 基础上的修改，而是对于最初的 Johnston Sans 的全盘复古。<br>…………<br><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">这就是字体界的原教旨主义，字体界的恐怖时代就要来了！</span></q></div>（最后一句话当然是在开玩笑）","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1177444","time":"2016-9-3 15:13","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"可惜内容很少？"}]}]